HSBC Hires Bankers to Advise on U.S. Card Unit Sale, Sky Reports

-- B y   B e n   L i v e s e y
-- 
2011-04-27T19:36:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/hsbc-hires-bankers-to-advise-on-u-s-card-unit-sale-sky-reports.html
HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  has hired bankers
to advise it on the sale of its U.S. credit card unit, Sky News
reported, without citing a source for the information.      HSBC plans to appoint a European bank to act as joint
broker alongside Goldman Sachs Group Inc. and is also close to
agreeing a joint venture in  China  that will enable it to
underwrite domestic share offerings, Sky said.    Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
